Others: The Utah Jazz lost to the Los Angeles Clippers, 105-116.
Keyonte George was benched by head coach Will Hardy in the third quarter due to poor defense in the first half.
Isaiah Collier filled in for George and had a career-high 26 minutes, posting four points, eight assists, and two steals.
George finished the game with 34 minutes, nine points, five rebounds, and three assists.
Coach Will Hardy emphasized the importance of creating good defensive habits for young players.
